The <java> task ignores the append attribute while redirecting the output and/or error to a file, 
since 1.6.0 (works fine with 1.5.4). output and error files are always overwritten.

It seems that the setAppend(boolean append) method in src/main/org/apache/tools/ant/taskdefs/ 
should be modified to replace ;

this.append = append;

with :

redirector.setAppend(append);
